import Home from './components/home/home'
import Login from './components/Login/login';

const routes =[
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Home",
        key: "home",
        route: "/home",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Alphabet",
        key: "alphabet",
        route: "/alphabet",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 1

    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Vocabulary",
        key: "vocab",
        route: "/vocab",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Sentences",
        key: "sent",
        route: "/sent",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Tenses",
        key: "tense",
        route: "/tense",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10

    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Reading",
        key: "read",
        route: "/read",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Writing",
        key: "write",
        route: "/write",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0
    }
];

export default routes;
